<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>PickEat 인증번호</title>
  <!--[if mso]>
  <style type="text/css">
    body, table, td {font-family: Arial, sans-serif !important;}
  </style>
  <![endif]-->
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #020617; font-family: 'Inter', 'Noto Sans KR', 'Pretendard Variable', system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;">
  <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #020617;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 20px;">
        <!-- Main Container -->
        <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="600" style="max-width: 600px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); border-radius: 32px; border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);">
          
          <!-- Header with Logo -->
          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 40px 20px 40px;">
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center">
                    <!-- Logo Box -->
                    <div style="display: inline-block; width: 64px; height: 64px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fb923c 0%, #ec4899 50%, #d946ef 100%); border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.3); margin-bottom: 16px;">
                      <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 100%; height: 100%; font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; color: #0f172a;">P</div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Brand Name -->
                    <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">PickEat</h1>
                    <p style="margin: 4px 0 0 0; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;">Recommendation OS</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <!-- Content -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 0 40px 40px 40px;">
              <!-- Title -->
              <h2 style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: #ffffff; text-align: center;">
                이메일 인증번호
              </h2>
              
              <!-- Description -->
              <p style="margin: 0 0 32px 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #cbd5e1; text-align: center;">
                PickEat 회원가입을 위한 인증번호입니다.<br>
                아래 인증번호를 입력해주세요.
              </p>
              <!-- Verification Code Box -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 0 auto 32px auto; background-color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6); border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center" style="padding: 32px 24px;">
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 500;">Verification Code</p>
                    <div style="display: inline-block; padding: 16px 32px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.2) 0%, rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.2) 50%, rgba(217, 70, 239, 0.2) 100%); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.3);">
                      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #ffffff; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;">
                        {{verificationCode}}
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              <!-- Info Box -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 0 auto; background-color: rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.1); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.2);">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 16px 20px;">
                    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; color: #fed7aa; text-align: center;">
                      ⏱️ 인증번호는 <strong style="color: #ffffff;">3분</strong>간 유효합니다.<br>
                      🔒 보안을 위해 인증번호를 타인에게 공유하지 마세요.
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 24px 40px 40px 40px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);">
              <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; text-align: center;">
                이 이메일은 PickEat 회원가입 요청으로 인해 발송되었습니다.
              </p>
              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 11px; color: #475569; text-align: center;">
                요청하지 않으셨다면 이 이메일을 무시하셔도 됩니다.
              </p>
              <p style="margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 11px; color: #64748b; text-align: center;">
                © 2024 PickEat. All rights reserved.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
